headline: Hormel Foods Seeking Nominations for 2025 Class of 10 Under 20 Food Heroes
summary: Hormel Foods Corporation (NYSE: HRL), a Fortune 500 global branded food company, is now accepting nominations for the 2025 class of 10 Under 20 Food Heroes. The impact-driven program, now in its fourth year, recognizes the efforts of young people across the United States who are contributing to a more sustainable food system — a system that produces and shares food in ways that uplift people and communities while nurturing the planet.
